bize asla zarar vermez.

602
00:42:45,880 --> 00:42:48,236
Lütfen Tink, güven bana.

603
00:42:51,080 --> 00:42:52,150
Ben kışa bakacağım.

604
00:42:53,920 --> 00:42:54,956
Hey, Tink!

605
00:42:56,320 --> 00:42:57,720
