630
00:47:09,440 --> 00:47:11,830
Bak Fawn, o iyi olacak...

631
00:47:12,600 --> 00:47:13,829
Fawn?

632
00:47:29,280 --> 00:47:30,280
Huysuz?

633
00:47:31,640 --> 00:47:33,040
Aşağı gel.

634
00:47:33,840 --> 00:47:35,593
Seni görmem gerek.

635
00:47:48,680 --> 00:47:49,750
Huysuz?

636
00:48:09,360 --> 00:48:10,430
Sıkı durun!

637
00:48:18,120 --> 00:48:19,236
Gece gölgesi tozu!

638
00:48:44,440 --> 00:48:46,272
Sabitleyin! Yere sağlam basın!

639
00:49:10,200 --> 00:49:11,759
Hadi onu götürelim!

